name: Label that Diagram - Human Sleleton 2 - Med
name_original: Label that Diagram - Human Sleleton 2 - Med
description:
This is a Windows program and will run on versions 7 through 11.  This program lets the user practice naming and learning the bones of the human body.  It goes into more detail than my earlier program on this topic.

The program is 100% free and can be installed on as many computers as you like and can be given freely to other people. The only restrictions are that it is not distributed for profit and it is not modified in any way.

The zipped setup program can be downloaded from these sources.

https://sites.google.com/view/rtcgames/home

https://itch.io/search?q=rtcgames
